# Windrose server (this repo)

Fork-style image from [indifferentbroccoli/windrose-server-docker](https://github.com/indifferentbroccoli/windrose-server-docker). Wine-based Windows server binary; **amd64** only. Align behavior with upstream unless intentionally changing DataKnife deployment.

## Official game server documentation

- [Dedicated Server Guide (Windrose)](https://playwindrose.com/dedicated-server-guide) — `ServerDescription.json` / `WorldDescription.json`, invite codes, ports, SteamCMD app id **4129620**, LAN + Docker / ICE caveats, Proxmox CPU `host`, experimental Linux+Wine notes.
- [Indifferent Broccolipedia](https://wiki.indifferentbroccoli.com) — general hosting patterns; [Windrose section](https://wiki.indifferentbroccoli.com/Windrose) for broccoli-specific guides.

When changing env vars or JSON-driven behavior, cross-check field names and semantics with the official guide (paths inside the container differ from a bare Windows install).

## Layout

- `scripts/` — `init.sh`, `start.sh`, Windrose+ / UE4SS helpers; `# shellcheck source=scripts/functions.sh` (paths resolve from repo root in CI).
- `Dockerfile` / `Dockerfile.staging` — Debian + Wine stable vs staging; CI runs Hadolint on **both**.
- `deploy/` — Kustomize (`deploy/base/`, root `deploy/kustomization.yaml`). Trial: `kubectl apply -k deploy/overlays/min-spec/` (namespace `game-servers`, needs Harbor pull secret). Default: `kubectl apply -k deploy/`. Dashboard port **8780**.
- `.github/actions/verify-game-server/` — same verify pipeline as Satisfactory sibling repo.

## Kubernetes

- Single PVC for `server-files`; optional Windrose+ dashboard exposure on 8780.
- For ICE/P2P edge cases on LAN + Kubernetes networking, see the Docker NAT section in the official dedicated server guide.
- **`docs/KUBERNETES.md`** — cluster notes (NFS / DepotDownloader, **ClusterIP**, Envoy + kube-vip, **EnvoyProxy**). **`deploy/envoy/`** — Envoy Gateway apply set. **`docs/examples/`** — placeholder reference YAML.

